Running rest and php benchmarks:

Inside ./rest directory: 

1. Install apache, create a symlink for the php files

$ sudo ln -s ./php-rest-service/ /var/www/service

2. Run benchmarks with make

$ make dynamic-benchmark
$ make json-benchmark
$ make static-benchmark
$ make rest-benchmark

3. That's all


Running thrift benchmarks

Inside ./thrift directory: 

1. Start server

$ make run-server &

2. Run benchmarks

$ make php-client-benchmark
$ make python-client-benchmark
